# Master Implementation Plan: The Human OS Evolution (Final)

This blueprint outlines the complete transformation of Jarvis into a state-of-the-art, human-like AI OS.

## 🎯 Project Goals
1.  **High Stability**: Intelligent fallbacks (Gemini -> Grok) and robust error handling for low-level sensors and speech loops.
2.  **Context Density**: Awareness of frontmost apps, visual state, and past conversation history.
3.  **Human Personality**: Fillers, emotional prosody, and a self-healing reinforcement loop.

---

## 🛠️ Proposed Changes

### [Phase 1] Foundation & Stability (The "Zero-Bug" Path)

#### [MODIFY] [main.py](file:///Users/lynux/Desktop/BackEnd/Startup/main.py)
 - **Greeting Sync**: Implement a `is_greeting_active` flag. Prevent the main `listen()` loop from starting until the background `daily_greeting` has completely finished. This fixes the startup "Didn't catch that" loop.

#### [MODIFY] [llm_brain.py](file:///Users/lynux/Desktop/BackEnd/Startup/core/llm_brain.py)
 - **Grok Fallback**: Implement automatic switching to xAI Grok API on Gemini 429/503 errors.
 - **Frontmost Awareness**: Inject focused Mac application name into every LLM prompt.

#### [MODIFY] [control/mac/briefing.py](file:///Users/lynux/Desktop/BackEnd/Startup/control/mac/briefing.py)
 - **Temperature Fix**: Filter out `0.0°C` dummy values. Add `sysctl` fallback to provide CPU info if sensors are locked.

#### [MODIFY] [core/thinking_ui.py](file:///Users/lynux/Desktop/BackEnd/Startup/core/thinking_ui.py)
 - **UI Artifact Fix**: Set `overrideredirect(False)` then immediately `True` or use `attributes("-type", "panel")` to prevent it from stealing focus or creating a new workspace entry on macOS.

#### [MODIFY] [fast_intent.py](file:///Users/lynux/Desktop/BackEnd/Startup/core/fast_intent.py)
 - **Intent Disambiguation**: Differentiate "screen" (visual) from "screen" (brightness). Add visual keywords ("seeing", "looking", "on my screen") to `take_screenshot`.

#### [MODIFY] [email_control.py](file:///Users/lynux/Desktop/BackEnd/Startup/control/email_control.py)
 - **Auth Recovery**: Implement `invalid_grant` detection to auto-reset OAuth tokens.

### [Phase 2] The Human Persona (The Soul)

#### [MODIFY] [llm_brain.py](file:///Users/lynux/Desktop/BackEnd/Startup/core/llm_brain.py)
 - **The Filler Engine**: Mandate natural fillers (`hmm`, `uh`, `...`) and emotional markers in responses.

#### [MODIFY] [memory.py](file:///Users/lynux/Desktop/BackEnd/Startup/core/memory.py)
 - **SemanticLogSearch**: Index and retrieve past interactions from `logs/` for long-term recall.

#### [MODIFY] [voice_response.py](file:///Users/lynux/Desktop/BackEnd/Startup/core/voice_response.py)
 - **Dynamic Prosody**: Link ElevenLabs "Stability" and "Style" settings to the current mood/sentiment.

### [Phase 3] Advanced OS Agents (The Muscles)

#### [NEW] [browser_agent.py](file:///Users/lynux/Desktop/BackEnd/Startup/core/agents/browser_agent.py)
 - Control Safari/Chrome tabs and navigation via AppleScript.

#### [NEW] [window_agent.py](file:///Users/lynux/Desktop/BackEnd/Startup/core/agents/window_agent.py)
 - Native Mac window layouts (Tiling, Resizing, Grid).

#### [MODIFY] [system_agent.py](file:///Users/lynux/Desktop/BackEnd/Startup/core/agents/system_agent.py)
 - Add `psutil`-based system diagnostics (CPU, RAM, Net) and OS toggles.

### [Phase 4] The Intelligence Loop (The Evolution)

#### [NEW] [supervisor.py](file:///Users/lynux/Desktop/BackEnd/Startup/core/supervisor.py)
 - **Background Watchdog**: Asynchronously verify intents against Gemini 1.5 Pro to identify misalignments.

#### [MODIFY] [reinforcement.py](file:///Users/lynux/Desktop/BackEnd/Startup/core/reinforcement.py)
 - **Silent Learning**: Auto-inject "Negative Examples" from Supervisor audits to heal the routing engine.

